---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import { SITE } from '../lib/site';
---

<Base
  title="Disclaimer | Elitas"
  description="Marketing disclaimer for the Elitas website and its project pages."
  theme="legacy"
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="ledger-head">
        <span class="mono-label">Legal</span>
        <span class="mono-label">Marketing disclaimer</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="display display-lg disc-title">Disclaimer</h1>

      <div class="disc-body">
        <p>
          This website is for general information only and does not constitute an offer, an
          invitation to offer, a commitment or a legal agreement of any kind. Nothing on this
          website shall be construed as a promise of sale, allotment, specification, amenity or
          timeline.
        </p>
        <p>
          All images, renders, walkthroughs, plans and visualisations on this website -
          including views of gardens, amenities, structures and landscapes - are
          <strong>artistic impressions for representation only</strong> and do not depict a
          completed or approved state of any project. Actual outcomes may differ.
        </p>
        <p>
          Plots offered are agricultural farm plots. Land in this region falls within the area
          governed by <strong>G.O. Ms. No. 111</strong> and construction on any plot, where
          undertaken, is optional and subject to the norms applicable to such land, including
          limits on built-up footprint. Any farm house designs shown are
          <strong>proposed concepts</strong>; no representation is made that any structure is
          sanctioned or approved. Buyers must independently verify the permissibility of any
          construction with the relevant authorities before proceeding.
        </p>
        <p>
          Areas, dimensions, distances and travel times mentioned on this website are
          approximate, based on third-party map services and site measurements, and are provided
          for convenience only. Registered extents include undivided shares in common areas as
          per the applicable documentation.
        </p>
        <p>
          Nothing on this website claims or implies registration of any project under the Real
          Estate (Regulation and Development) Act, 2016, nor approval of any layout by HMDA,
          DTCP or any other authority, unless expressly stated with the relevant number.
        </p>
        <p>
          Prospective buyers are advised to seek independent legal advice and to rely solely on
          the definitive transaction documents executed between the parties. For current
          information, contact us at {SITE.phoneDisplay}.
        </p>
        <p class="disc-note mono-data">
          THIS DISCLAIMER IS A DRAFT PENDING REVIEW BY ELITAS'S LEGAL ADVISORS.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .disc-title {
    margin-bottom: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
  }

  .disc-body p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    max-width: 46em;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .disc-body strong {
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .disc-note {
    color: var(--laterite);
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    padding-top: 1rem;
  }
</style>
